    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. some people I've talked to say that even with the risks, it's basically the only way we're actually going to hit our net zero goals in time. like, renewables alone can't do it, right? do you think the scale of the climate crisis makes the risks of nuclear more acceptable?",
