    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty strong stance. but what about the people who argue that we should be focusing all that money on storage tech and smart grids instead? isn't it a bit risky to double down on something that has such massive waste and safety issues when we could be perfecting the cleaner options?",
